Package src.Boundary.Mains.Staff

Class StaffTypeMain

java.lang.Object
src.Boundary.Mains.Staff.StaffTypeMain
All Implemented Interfaces:
IMain
public class StaffTypeMain extends Object implements IMain
The StaffTypeMain class represents the main entry point and user interaction handler for staff-type users in the CAMs Registration System. It allows staff members to access and manage their own camps, reports, suggestions, and inquiries.
